description.secret: Aragog is the 1st VM of 3-box HarryPotter VM series in which you need to find 2 horcruxes hidden inside the machine (total 8 horcruxes hidden across 3 VMs of the HarryPotter Series) and ultimately defeat Voldemort.
description.note:
This works better with VirtualBox rather than VMware
